statements: SELECT * FROM daily_calorie_intake;
SELECT total_calories, protein_grams, carbs_grams, fat_grams FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE total_calories > 2000 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT user_id, SUM(total_calories) AS total_calories_sum FROM daily_calorie_intake GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, date, total_calories FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE total_calories > 2000 ORDER BY date ASC;
SELECT user_id, total_calories FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE protein_grams > 50 AND carbs_grams < 100 ORDER BY total_calories DESC;
SELECT user_id, date, protein_grams FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE fat_grams > 30 ORDER BY user_id, date DESC;
SELECT user_id, date, total_calories, protein_grams, carbs_grams, fat_grams FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE total_calories BETWEEN 1500 AND 1800 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT user_id, date, total_calories, protein_grams, carbs_grams, fat_grams FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE user_id = 3 OR total_calories < 2000 ORDER BY total_calories ASC, date DESC;
SELECT * FROM calorie_intake;
SELECT date, total_calories FROM calorie_intake ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT * FROM macronutrient_distribution WHERE protein_g > 50 AND fats_g < 20;
SELECT date, protein_g, carbs_g, fats_g FROM macronutrient_distribution ORDER BY protein_g DESC, date ASC;
SELECT date, total_calories FROM calorie_intake WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT date, total_calories FROM calorie_intake WHERE total_calories > 2000 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT date, protein_g, carbs_g, fats_g FROM macronutrient_distribution WHERE protein_g > 50 AND carbs_g < 100 ORDER BY fats_g ASC, date DESC;
SELECT date, total_calories FROM calorie_intake UNION SELECT date, protein_g FROM macronutrient_distribution ORDER BY date;
SELECT date, protein_g, carbs_g, fats_g FROM macronutrient_distribution WHERE fats_g > 15 ORDER BY protein_g DESC, date ASC;

SELECT date, total_calories, carbs_g FROM calorie_intake JOIN macronutrient_distribution ON calorie_intake.date = macronutrient_distribution.date WHERE total_calories < 1500 AND protein_g > 40 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT * FROM DailyCalorieIntake;
SELECT date, total_calories FROM DailyCalorieIntake ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT food_name, calories FROM FoodConsumption WHERE date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT date, protein_g, carbs_g, fats_g FROM MacronutrientDistribution WHERE protein_g > 50;
SELECT SUM(total_calories) AS total_calories_consumed FROM DailyCalorieIntake;
SELECT * FROM DailyCalorieIntake WHERE total_calories > 2000;
SELECT date, protein_g, carbs_g, fats_g FROM MacronutrientDistribution ORDER BY date DESC;

SELECT SUM(calories) AS total_calories_consumed, SUM(protein_g) AS total_protein_consumed, SUM(carbs_g) AS total_carbs_consumed, SUM(fats_g) AS total_fats_consumed FROM FoodConsumption GROUP BY date HAVING total_calories_consumed > 1500;
SELECT date, food_name, calories FROM FoodConsumption WHERE protein_g > 20 AND carbs_g < 50 ORDER BY date ASC, calories DESC;
SELECT date, AVG(total_calories) AS avg_calories_intake FROM DailyCalorieIntake GROUP BY date HAVING avg_calories_intake < 1800;
SELECT * FROM daily_calorie_intake;
SELECT date, total_calories FROM daily_calorie_intake WHERE total_calories > 2000;
SELECT food_name, calories, protein_grams FROM food_diary ORDER BY calories DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_profile WHERE age < 30 AND height > 170;
SELECT plan_id, plan_name, total_calories, total_protein FROM meal_plan WHERE total_protein >= 100;
SELECT * FROM daily_calorie_intake ORDER BY date DESC, total_calories ASC
SELECT food_name, calories FROM food_diary WHERE protein_grams > 20 AND carbs_grams < 50
SELECT username, daily_calorie_goal FROM user_profile WHERE age >= 30
SELECT * FROM meal_plan WHERE total_protein >= 100 AND total_carbs <= 150 ORDER BY total_calories DESC
SELECT date, SUM(total_calories) AS total_calories_consumed FROM daily_calorie_intake GROUP BY date HAVING total_calories_consumed > 2000
SELECT * FROM Users;
SELECT name, age FROM Users ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT meal_name, calories FROM Meals WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT food_name, protein, carbs FROM Food WHERE calories < 100 AND fat < 5;
SELECT report_date, calories_consumed, protein_consumed, carbs_consumed, fat_consumed FROM Daily_Report WHERE user_id = 2 ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT Users.name, Users.age, Meals.meal_name, Meals.calories FROM Users JOIN Meals ON Users.id = Meals.user_id WHERE Users.age > 30 ORDER BY Meals.calories DESC

SELECT Users.name, Food_Log.log_date, Food.food_name, Food_Log.quantity FROM Users JOIN Food_Log ON Users.id = Food_Log.user_id JOIN Food ON Food_Log.food_id = Food.food_id WHERE Food.calories < 500 ORDER BY Food_Log.log_date ASC

SELECT Users.name, Meals.meal_time, Meals.meal_name, Food.calories, Food.protein FROM Users JOIN Meals ON Users.id = Meals.user_id JOIN Food ON Meals.calories = Food.calories AND Meals.protein = Food.protein WHERE Users.name LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY Meals.meal_time DESC

SELECT Daily_Report.report_date, Users.name, Food_Log.quantity FROM Daily_Report JOIN Users ON Daily_Report.user_id = Users.id JOIN Food_Log ON Daily_Report.user_id = Food_Log.user_id WHERE Daily_Report.calories_consumed > 2000 ORDER BY Daily_Report.report_date ASC
SELECT Users.name, SUM(Food_Log.quantity) AS total_quantity FROM Users JOIN Food_Log ON Users.id = Food_Log.user_id GROUP BY Users.name HAVING total_quantity > 10 ORDER BY total_quantity DESC
